oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Church Avenue
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Thompson Brothers
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Church Avenue, Knoxville, TN. Ca. 1926. Ross Flats at left with signs for Dr. McIlwaine, Dr. Cunningham, and Dr. Oppenheimer. Old Church Street Methodist Church. Construction of Tennessee General Building. F.M. George truck at right. Cars parked on street.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Streets; Apartment houses; Trucks; Automobiles; Methodist churches;
